node.text:
does a bed count as a desk? is school now just a chat room filled with faces? these are confusing times. and the Impossible™️ Whopper makes things, well, a little more confusing. 

@impossible_foods

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Burger King on July 15, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: pssttt, hey we’re trying to tell you something

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Burger King on July 13, 2021. May be an image of french fries and text that says 'HAPPY NATIONAL FRENCH FRY DAY ZA'.

node.text:
the greatest part about free fries? the possibility of that lone o-ring. purchase $1 or more on the BK app or at bk.com and get a free order of medium french fries. 

at part. U.S. restaurants. terms at bk.com/terms
